{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"57251ab739","title":"甘南县移民骚动情况续志","origin":"新华社《内部参考》1956年5月31日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1a002bfdd9","index":0,"year":1956,"month":5,"day":31,"articleId":"57251ab739"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0e02b19bae","type":"title","text":"甘南县移民骚动情况续志","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"57251ab739"},{"id":"47c970b2f6","type":"paragraph","text":"【新华社哈尔滨31日讯】嫩江、齐齐哈尔市和各县、市机关、部队、学校共抽调五千多名干部，在27日前分五批下乡，把甘南县骚动起来的四千五百多名山东移民阻挡回村。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"57251ab739"},{"id":"d57deaa056","type":"paragraph","text":"在动员移民回村途中，嫩江专署公安处，非正式地逮捕了三十二个骚动的带头人，县公安局也捕了一批人。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"57251ab739"},{"id":"c733950734","type":"paragraph","text":"现在干部正在乡下帮助移民返原籍，当地领导干部认为“可以向移民说，愿走者则走，愿留者则留。这样做，要比目前动员移民回村的做法在政治和经济上的损失要少一些”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"57251ab739"},{"id":"eae6cba77a","type":"paragraph","text":" （任永达）","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"57251ab739"}],"page":{"id":"c7d5aa9380","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"57251ab739","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}